  "general_information": "The MARVEL EAGLE is a 299.9m LNG carrier built by Kawasaki Heavy Industries, Ltd. in Japan for Mitsui O.S.K. Lines, Ltd. It features a high-performance ship operation data collection device and is equipped with a dual-fuel propulsion system. The vessel has a capacity of 156,059m^3 and will be used to service the Cameron LNG project in Louisiana.",
